1
00:00:03,080 --> 00:00:05,350
♪But no matter how passionate we were♪

2
00:00:05,350 --> 00:00:07,060
♪No matter how resolute the past♪

3
00:00:07,060 --> 00:00:10,720
♪It was all a fictional plot♪

4
00:00:11,230 --> 00:00:14,150
♪The vow named 'forever' turned into a lie♪

5
00:00:14,150 --> 00:00:17,180
♪Changed long ago with time♪

6
00:00:17,180 --> 00:00:19,720
♪Gradually disintegrated♪

7
00:00:20,080 --> 00:00:23,280
♪When memories are revisited in the deep night♪

8
00:00:23,600 --> 00:00:26,860
♪It feels like we still have everything♪

9
00:00:27,120 --> 00:00:29,130
♪But upon realization♪

10
00:00:29,130 --> 00:00:32,420
♪The story has ended hastily♪

11
00:00:32,670 --> 00:00:36,230
♪Flickering on and off♪

12
00:00:36,580 --> 00:00:47,140
=Chasing Love=

13
00:00:47,380 --> 00:00:51,180
=Episode 12=

14
00:00:53,340 --> 00:00:54,180
Open the door.

15
00:00:56,140 --> 00:00:58,800
Master, what happened?

16
00:00:59,480 --> 00:01:00,560
Who is this?

17
00:01:01,200 --> 00:01:02,040
Qin Jifeng.

18
00:01:03,010 --> 00:01:05,390
No, now he should be called Liang Jifeng.

19
00:01:05,800 --> 00:01:07,480
- Find a day to change your surname
- Liang Jifeng.

20
00:01:07,480 --> 00:01:08,480
and return to the clan.

21
00:01:09,580 --> 00:01:12,320
My son should not take his mother's surname.

22
00:01:14,470 --> 00:01:15,400
Understood, Father.

23
00:01:16,260 --> 00:01:17,920
Master, where is Jiahao?

24
00:01:18,280 --> 00:01:19,400
Where did Jiahao go, Master?

25
00:01:19,400 --> 00:01:21,770
Don't mention your useless son.

26
00:01:22,910 --> 00:01:27,340
He pointed a gun at his head to threaten me.

27
00:01:28,190 --> 00:01:30,700
I don't have such a rebellious son.

28
00:01:30,890 --> 00:01:33,440
He wouldn't lose to an illegitimate son,
Master?

29
00:01:37,820 --> 00:01:39,380
Listen to me carefully.

30
00:01:40,480 --> 00:01:42,970
Jifeng is my son.

31
00:01:43,600 --> 00:01:46,320
If I hear you say that again,

32
00:01:46,960 --> 00:01:48,480
don't blame me for being rude.

33
00:01:51,840 --> 00:01:53,020
Jiahao.

34
00:01:54,980 --> 00:01:57,840
Jiahao, where did you go?

35
00:01:58,240 --> 00:01:59,520
Jiahao.

36
00:02:08,650 --> 00:02:09,800
Jiahao.

37
00:02:14,020 --> 00:02:16,540
(Hongcheng Hotel)

38
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:17,800
- Yue
- Water.

39
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:21,040
- Yue, you must hold on.
- Water.

40
00:02:23,720 --> 00:02:24,800
Water.

41
00:02:27,480 --> 00:02:28,560
Water.

42
00:02:50,320 --> 00:02:51,160
No.

43
00:02:51,420 --> 00:02:52,440
The fever is severe.

44
00:02:53,480 --> 00:02:54,400
I need to get some medicine.

45
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:59,280
♪Lingering and gazing♪

46
00:03:03,680 --> 00:03:04,640
Go, go, go.

47
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:05,800
Hurry, move aside.

48
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:07,640
(Xingrui Medical Clinic)
No money to pay for the medicine?

49
00:03:07,640 --> 00:03:08,880
Do you think this is a charity hall?

50
00:03:10,880 --> 00:03:12,440
Ladies and gentlemen, don't miss out.

51
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:13,840
Don't push.

52
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:15,160
Everyone will get some. Here. Here.

53
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:17,160
One at a time.

54
00:03:17,160 --> 00:03:18,520
Today is our pharmacy's anniversary.

55
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:19,960
Free clinic and free medicine.

56
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:21,360
Free medical consultations.

57
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:22,320
Free medicine.

58
00:03:22,640 --> 00:03:25,360
Whether you have a fever, a cold,
or a headache.

59
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:27,760
Genuine medicine at fair prices.

60
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:29,640
Alright, here, take it.

61
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:31,360
We guarantee genuine medicine at fair prices.

62
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:32,920
The event ends today.

63
00:03:32,920 --> 00:03:34,160
Don't miss out. It won't happen again.

64
00:03:34,160 --> 00:03:35,400
Come, take a look.

65
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:41,920
♪No time to weigh gains and losses♪

66
00:03:42,130 --> 00:03:43,640
Doctor, how is she?

67
00:03:45,760 --> 00:03:46,960
Follow the prescription I gave you.

68
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:47,800
Three times a day.

69
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:48,920
She'll get better soon.

70
00:03:50,280 --> 00:03:51,280
Thank you, sir.

71
00:03:52,610 --> 00:03:55,170
♪We met too late♪

72
00:03:55,200 --> 00:03:56,080
Take care.

73
00:03:56,310 --> 00:04:02,250
♪When feelings grow, we often have to part♪

74
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:06,080
♪Life is too cold ♪

75
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:08,480
Yue, you're awake.

76
00:04:10,350 --> 00:04:17,050
♪How can fragile petals
withstand the harsh snow♪

77
00:04:17,460 --> 00:04:21,420
♪The dancing light takes away the brilliance♪

78
00:04:23,120 --> 00:04:24,480
Why did you save me?

79
00:04:27,200 --> 00:04:28,360
Your dad

80
00:04:30,200 --> 00:04:31,520
killed my dad.

81
00:04:31,520 --> 00:04:35,630
♪Only regret remains♪

82
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:40,800
I'm sorry.

83
00:04:44,500 --> 00:04:45,800
My father wronged you.

84
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:51,280
Your dad killed my dad.

85
00:04:51,940 --> 00:04:54,280
Do you know how much I hate him,

86
00:04:54,680 --> 00:04:56,330
how much I want revenge

87
00:04:56,350 --> 00:04:58,760
and how much I want to kill him
with my own hands?

88
00:04:59,330 --> 00:05:00,850
I know. I know it all.

89
00:05:02,030 --> 00:05:03,270
Let's leave this place, okay?

90
00:05:03,580 --> 00:05:04,480
Go far away.

91
00:05:04,860 --> 00:05:06,990
Forget the Governor's Mansion
and the Fortune Trading Company.

92
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:08,880
Those burdens shouldn't be ours to bear.

93
00:05:09,850 --> 00:05:10,920
I just want to be with you.

94
00:05:11,400 --> 00:05:12,800
And live a peaceful life.

95
00:05:17,530 --> 00:05:19,550
Where can we go?

96
00:05:24,770 --> 00:05:25,980
I can do business

97
00:05:26,280 --> 00:05:27,360
or work as a laborer.

98
00:05:29,080 --> 00:05:30,760
I can give you the life you want.

99
00:05:31,550 --> 00:05:34,360
♪Happy times are too short♪

100
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:36,400
Trust me.

101
00:05:38,640 --> 00:05:44,710
♪When feelings grow, we often have to part♪

102
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:46,480
Your hand is wounded.

103
00:05:48,200 --> 00:05:49,880
Let me bandage it for you first.

104
00:05:52,550 --> 00:05:55,420
♪How can fragile petals♪

105
00:05:55,640 --> 00:05:56,770
Yue.

106
00:05:58,400 --> 00:05:59,840
I've finally got to be with you.

107
00:05:59,840 --> 00:06:03,950
♪The dancing light takes away the brilliance♪

108
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:05,840
(Where can we go?)

109
00:06:06,880 --> 00:06:08,240
(This vast net of Hongcheng)

110
00:06:08,520 --> 00:06:10,960
(has already deeply entangled us.)

111
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:16,200
Don't worry. It's nothing serious.

112
00:06:18,360 --> 00:06:20,160
Don't tell anyone about what happened today.

113
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:25,920
Boss, the boat is ready.

114
00:06:29,300 --> 00:06:30,290
Yue is meticulous.

115
00:06:30,690 --> 00:06:31,960
Don't let her find out it was me.

116
00:06:32,970 --> 00:06:33,810
Alright.

117
00:06:41,880 --> 00:06:45,240
Jifeng, these are what we usually eat.

118
00:06:45,880 --> 00:06:47,760
I don't know if you can get used to it.

119
00:06:48,210 --> 00:06:49,640
If you can't get used to it,

120
00:06:49,770 --> 00:06:51,160
I'll prepare something else for you.

121
00:06:51,880 --> 00:06:53,960
Thank you, Mrs. Chen.
This is already good enough.

122
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:56,200
Jifeng,

123
00:06:56,860 --> 00:06:58,530
we're all family. No need to be so formal.

124
00:06:58,890 --> 00:06:59,840
And you just came back.

125
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:01,900
If there's anything you're not used to,

126
00:07:02,270 --> 00:07:03,320
just tell her,

127
00:07:04,250 --> 00:07:05,220
and let her arrange it for you.

128
00:07:06,270 --> 00:07:07,110
Thank you, Father.

129
00:07:08,920 --> 00:07:09,760
Let's eat.

130
00:07:10,080 --> 00:07:10,920
Alright.

131
00:07:12,780 --> 00:07:13,620
By the way, Jifeng,

132
00:07:16,370 --> 00:07:18,980
there's something I need you to do today.

133
00:07:21,940 --> 00:07:22,880
Father, just give the order.

134
00:07:25,210 --> 00:07:27,140
Go to the Newspaper Office
and publish a front-page article.

135
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:30,280
Fortune Trading Company is caught
smuggling arms.

136
00:07:31,360 --> 00:07:34,640
Starting today,
seal the banks and detain all ships.

137
00:07:36,440 --> 00:07:38,080
Yes, I will handle it right away.

138
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:41,060
Sit down.

139
00:07:41,630 --> 00:07:42,520
Finish your meal first.

140
00:07:42,520 --> 00:07:43,600
before you go handle the matter.

141
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:45,080
Yes, Father.

142
00:07:47,200 --> 00:07:48,040
Silly child.

143
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:51,920
This silly child.

144
00:07:55,780 --> 00:07:57,520
(Fortune Trading Company caught smuggling arms)

145
00:07:57,550 --> 00:07:59,300
(Its owner Ouyang Zhongtian suspected
to be involved)

146
00:08:33,220 --> 00:08:34,460
(To Governor Liang)

147
00:08:57,020 --> 00:08:57,860
Mr. Jifeng,

148
00:08:59,200 --> 00:09:01,990
Master asked me to give you the intelligence
we received this morning.

149
00:09:01,990 --> 00:09:04,920
It shows the hotel where Miss Ouyang
and Mr. Jiahao are hiding.

150
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:08,360
Master wants you to personally lead a team

151
00:09:08,680 --> 00:09:09,960
and capture Miss Ouyang.

152
00:09:15,680 --> 00:09:16,520
Understood.

153
00:09:18,120 --> 00:09:20,560
Master wants you to go now.

154
00:09:27,920 --> 00:09:29,520
Are you teaching me how to do things?

155
00:09:31,080 --> 00:09:31,920
I wouldn't dare.

156
00:09:36,160 --> 00:09:37,000
Lieutenant Li,

157
00:09:39,320 --> 00:09:40,880
you used to follow Jiahao,

158
00:09:41,760 --> 00:09:43,320
and had to listen to him for everything.

159
00:09:44,760 --> 00:09:46,240
But now that I'm back,

160
00:09:47,550 --> 00:09:51,050
you should know what you can do

161
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:52,920
and what you cannot.

162
00:09:53,680 --> 00:09:54,520
Got it?

163
00:09:55,640 --> 00:09:56,960
Yes, Mr. Jifeng.

164
00:09:58,120 --> 00:09:58,960
Let's go.

165
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:07,800
I got two tickets from my classmate.

166
00:10:10,510 --> 00:10:11,910
Let's head south.

167
00:10:18,300 --> 00:10:19,820
You said you like the sea.

168
00:10:20,360 --> 00:10:22,920
Find a warm place to stay by the seaside.

169
00:10:24,800 --> 00:10:26,000
I'll find some work.

170
00:10:26,660 --> 00:10:28,320
You can raise some flowers at home.

171
00:10:29,160 --> 00:10:30,450
When there's nothing to do,

172
00:10:31,520 --> 00:10:33,080
we can take a walk on the beach.

173
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:37,010
Jiahao.

174
00:10:39,730 --> 00:10:40,680
Yes?

175
00:10:44,720 --> 00:10:45,560
Nothing.

176
00:10:46,480 --> 00:10:49,640
I just thought we might not come back.

177
00:10:50,360 --> 00:10:51,360
It makes me sad.

178
00:10:57,880 --> 00:10:59,720
Everything will start anew.

179
00:11:07,280 --> 00:11:08,160
Jiahao,

180
00:11:11,360 --> 00:11:12,540
I just remembered

181
00:11:12,550 --> 00:11:14,930
I haven't picked up a photo of Father and me
at the photo studio.

182
00:11:15,720 --> 00:11:16,720
I need to get it back.

183
00:11:18,160 --> 00:11:19,000
I'll get it for you.

184
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:20,320
Wait for me.

185
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:25,080
Jiahao.

186
00:11:28,520 --> 00:11:29,360
What's wrong?

187
00:11:32,360 --> 00:11:33,360
Be careful on the road.

188
00:11:58,800 --> 00:12:00,000
Rickshaw.

189
00:12:00,680 --> 00:12:01,520
Madam,

190
00:12:01,640 --> 00:12:02,600
take a look.

191
00:12:02,880 --> 00:12:04,480
Freshly baked cakes.

192
00:12:06,680 --> 00:12:08,560
(Yue is acting a bit strange today.)

193
00:12:09,480 --> 00:12:10,920
Take a look.

194
00:12:43,970 --> 00:12:44,920
Yue.

195
00:12:46,960 --> 00:12:47,800
Yue!

196
00:12:59,890 --> 00:13:02,850
♪The streetlight's glow falls on the ground♪

197
00:13:03,370 --> 00:13:06,610
♪Your silhouette blurs and fades away♪

198
00:13:06,900 --> 00:13:09,450
♪I'm stranded in place♪

199
00:13:09,680 --> 00:13:12,590
♪Love and hate linger on my lips♪

200
00:13:12,590 --> 00:13:14,420
♪Time pushes away♪

201
00:13:14,430 --> 00:13:16,660
♪The distance between us♪

202
00:13:16,670 --> 00:13:17,410
♪Is enlarged♪

203
